data.description: Great 2 story in prime location. 4 beds, 3 bath, full unfinished basement, plenty of storage, even a laundry chute. Formal Living room and dining room for entertaining. Country kitchen with open concept to family room with fireplace and built in shelves. Large backyard with privacy fence and beautifully landscaped. Additional large room on main floor waiting to be finished to your liking. Along with a mud room to the house. Very spacious master bedroom with bath. Additional unfinished room off master bedroom that could be used as a study/office/gym. A deep 2 1/2 car garage with pull down stair for more storage. Even its own sub breaker box. New roof in 08, new A/C in 2003, many more updates. Possible related living options. The possibilities are endless. Rent to own or rental at $1800/mo are an option. Call for details
